{"tid":1251614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"6月23日（日） 20:00-21:30  立法會示威區  追究警察濫權集會","createTime":"2019-06-22T15:11:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T11:57:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"46909a5ed465e54a5dda1f71644337b66a7f5169","tid":1251614,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T15:11:52.000Z","msg":"6月23日（日）<br />\n20:00-21:30 <br />\n立法會示威區 <br />\n追究警察濫權集會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n民間人權陣線 Civil Human Rights Front<br />\n<br />\n已讚好的專頁 &middot; 2 小時 &middot; <br />\n <br />\n追究警察濫權 暴力鎮壓市民<br />\n<br />\nG20前夕集會另見︰<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Y8MCwo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Y8MCwo&d=ahpQ5aMQEo4h8Mt%2B3j6t3okJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=c361ebbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Y8MCwo</a><br />\n<br />\n香港市民為了引起社會關注，參與反送中示威運動，過程中中受到警方暴力對待。從69及612事件中，警方制度以及文化的腐敗表露無遺。我們希望從現有香港制度對警方作出投訴、同時也會透過國際間的渠道，把香港警察的濫權情況帶到國際，讓港府面對國際壓力！<br />\n<br />\n追究警察濫權集會<br />\n日期：6月23日（日）<br />\n地點：立法會示威區<br />\n時間：20:00-21:30<br />\n<br />\n發言嘉賓：<br />\n<br />\n曾健超(七警案當事人)<br />\n鄭仲恆(朱經緯案當事人)<br />\n法律界<br />\n葉寬柔 (香港人權監察)<br />\n<br />\n民間人權陣線秘書處<br />\n2019年6月22日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/65093866_2316792538368124_6753282486035283968_n.png?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_oc=AQmBqGiVcOP7Rss2EzvsXbx78WRJJBB_Klqz-u4yAri8fEzPzGt9lO4fHLfFqdCQ6C4&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-2.xx&amp;oh=de045f32beb9c8d7ae065edfa384cac5&amp;oe=5D7BC995\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F65093866_2316792538368124_6753282486035283968_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_oc%3DAQmBqGiVcOP7Rss2EzvsXbx78WRJJBB_Klqz-u4yAri8fEzPzGt9lO4fHLfFqdCQ6C4%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-2.xx%26oh%3Dde045f32beb9c8d7ae065edfa384cac5%26oe%3D5D7BC995&h=9a8d0679&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/photos/a.517931904920872/2316792535034791/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCivilHumanRightsFront%2Fphotos%2Fa.517931904920872%2F2316792535034791%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=ahpQ5aMQEo4h8Mt%2B3j6t3okJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=456874bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/photos/a.517931904920872/2316792535034791/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"e2fcf4c92114ed394a21c4337252c2e01428f0da","tid":1251614,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T15:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1d2d267922c43a4e3b8f78c726fb1ac0f5f8ac2","tid":1251614,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T15:13:54.000Z","msg":"聽晚"},{"pid":"4abae1483b81402b15e7d851665be312e66bbfea","tid":1251614,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T15:14:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7a2014424f984f670f8450d121a7f39a7adde1","tid":1251614,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:29:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c89e7143bfd2ee22884b16ef1d5014d82d0b04af","tid":1251614,"uid":235796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T07:30:03.000Z","msg":"重要事項：流水佔領（星期一）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1252567\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1252567</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"618d1557a7a91f367ffa7f135d6de08962f7424b","tid":1251614,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T09:16:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"32a7894112bafdf3112104407a2b384102cc5e93","tid":1251614,"uid":28870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T09:17:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19afa34254278557253babb5a300d34b17f9aa55","tid":1251614,"uid":231040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T09:18:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iQXj8Ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiQXj8Ad.jpg&h=cd49b3c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家經歷過這兩星期的抗爭運動都辛苦了! 雖然「五大訴求」(包括埋「林鄭下台」)仍然未達到，但希望大家趁呢兩日先好好地休息，之後重新裝備再齊齊繼續抗爭吧~<br />\n<br />\n不過，有啲事就真係比較急嘅，就係 - <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">距離今屆新選民登記嘅截止日期<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>仲剩番10日咋</strong></span>!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果你自己、兄弟姐妹、同事朋友等等仲未登記嘅，請好好把握今次嘅機會立即登記，以便喺<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: violet;\">今年24/11嘅區議會選舉</span></ins></span> 同 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: pink;\">出年立法會選舉</span></ins></strong></span>，將一個一個賣港又冇立場嘅親共政棍跟尾狗狠狠地踢出議會，將議會嘅否決權還番俾人民吧!!!<br />\n(可惜嘅係，已登記選民嘅更改資料期限已經喺2/6結束了，但大家仍需要覆查自己嘅選民資料有冇俾人更改／刪除咗，尤其係最近換咗新身分證嘅朋友)<br />\n<br />\n有關選民登記嘅資料如下：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">《地方選區選民》</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C&d=ahpQ5aMQEo4h8Mt%2B3j6t3okJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=ba4f7064\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C</a>).pdf<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">《功能界別選民及／或選舉委員會界別分組選民》</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-41%28C&d=ahpQ5aMQEo4h8Mt%2B3j6t3okJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=dbd93775\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C</a>).pdf<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">網上更新電郵地址</span></strong> - <a href=\"https://www.ospprdtwdc.reo.gov.hk/osp/ra008/mainEM.jsp&hellip;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ospprdtwdc.reo.gov.hk%2Fosp%2Fra008%2FmainEM.jsp%E2%80%A6&d=ahpQ5aMQEo4h8Mt%2B3j6t3okJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=73189f89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ospprdtwdc.reo.gov.hk/osp/ra008/mainEM.jsp&hellip;</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">選民資料網上查閱系統</span></span></strong> - <a href=\"https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fweb%2F&d=ahpQ5aMQEo4h8Mt%2B3j6t3okJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=a073bf4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/</a></span><br />\n<br />\n此外，資料組嘅朋友可以好好地利用呢段時間，儲齊呢段時間來班建制狗所做嘅「好人好事」並作出整理，成為「彈藥」以供文宣組嘅朋友製作長輩圖及其他文案等，對一眾被利用嘅中年／老人家作出「反洗腦」宣傳，辛苦大家了！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>＊＊＊ <span style=\"color: pink;\">齊心登記</span>，<span style=\"color: pink;\">一齊投票</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">用選票拆散保皇狗</span> ＊＊＊</strong></span>"},{"pid":"55ad7852f848d1d1f010282b1a7c0fef9126b0d5","tid":1251614,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T11:50:26.000Z","msg":"見到 都有唔算少人去緊"},{"pid":"1d5c946f041a4c9e51cf1a11e8fbaa3f4e11ef47","tid":1251614,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T11:54:55.000Z","msg":"現場<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vOFBs1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvOFBs1b.jpg&h=3a6ef747&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QApiGmd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQApiGmd.jpg&h=05992b3f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31aea1b642d8bc61144606531d4136ebe95ab8ee","tid":1251614,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T11:57:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G502oAo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG502oAo.jpg&h=ef7d89a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YzrAJAq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.l